{"tid":1242804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後無number無委託證既當冒警處理","createTime":"2019-06-19T07:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:58:05.000Z","uid":196751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb63beab7d0f0bf4dd31a4b237c691511d12b7bc","tid":1242804,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85b73a9c85535b3666ad1d90ad5829fbe867982","tid":1242804,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf06a3a6bb39016407b317771d1a9b9b94e7853","tid":1242804,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bf9503cadc12abe8141d2fcbc0661461dcb96c","tid":1242804,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9da622480471aa0bdd81a0ab6e5956d33e798a1","tid":1242804,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"委任證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de159d83d1bcc698fdfcd76af9a378c4634bd4b","tid":1242804,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"冇number都可以執行職務<br />\n咁市民去淘寶買件便衣黑背心褸都可以週街打人啦"},{"pid":"d2692c7e93a8e8eb7c6021d09cb9281530558869","tid":1242804,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fda58285668103b15904a50ee3713ef2f8b2f74","tid":1242804,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"大家識玩喇，全民著黑背心，個個好似便衣咁撚樣"}]}